Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
undo(25.10)                                                        undo(25.10)

Name
       undo  -  Undoes  the previous edit made with any bump placement, floor-
       planning, power planning, or wire edit commands listed below

Syntax
       undo [-help]

       Undoes the previous edit made with any bump  placement,  floorplanning,
       power planning, or wire edit commands listed below.

              * Selected bump placement commands:

                * create_bump

                * deleteBumps

              * Selected floorplanning commands:

                * alignObject

                * flipOrRotateObject

                * setObjFPlanBox

                * setObjFPlanBoxList

                * setObjFPlanPolygon

                * snapFPlan

                * snapFPlanIO

                * spaceObject

              * Selected power planning commands:

                * addRing

                * addStripe

                * editPowerVia

                * sroute

              *

                All wire editor commands:

                *

                  editAddFillet

                * editAddPoly

                *

                  editAddRoute

                *

                  editAddTrimMetal

              *

                * editAddVia

                * editChangeLayer

                * editChangeNet

                * editChangeRule

                * editChangeStatus

                * editChangeVia

                * editCommitPoly

                * editCommitRoute

                * editCutWire

                * editDelete

                * editDeleteFillet

                * editDeselect

                * editDuplicate

                * editFixWideWires

                * editMerge

                * editMove

                * editRotate

                * editSelect

                * editSplit

                * editResize

                * editTrim

                * prepareForEcoRoute

       You  can  use  the  redo command to redo an edit that was reversed with
       undo.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the undo command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man undo

Related Information
              * redo

              * Edit Menu chapter in the Menu Reference

                * Undo

                * Redo

